{"title":"Zerotier——内网穿透神器 for free","uid":"913a88b1308a2ce8d0499d200801961e","slug":"Zerotier——内网穿透神器-for-free","date":"2024-03-05T15:26:29.000Z","updated":"2024-11-04T05:31:50.250Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Zerotier——内网穿透神器-for-free.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/TwgbUuEPVxQO7oC.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Zerotier简介\"><a href=\"#Zerotier简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Zerotier简介\"></a>Zerotier简介</h1><p>zerotier是一个异地组网的solution，可以进行内网穿透从而实现远程办公，将公司、学校、家里的设备牢牢控制在自己手心里。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Zerotier安装\"><a href=\"#Zerotier安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Zerotier安装\"></a>Zerotier安装</h1><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zerotier.com/\">zerotier官网</a></p>\n\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"zerotier-center配置\"><a href=\"#zerotier-center配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zerotier center配置\"></a>zerotier center配置</h1><p>在zerotier官网打开<strong>Get ZeroTier</strong><br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/TGKveifLE21H8ua.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 140417.png\"><br>登录账户后会显示如下界面,点击<strong>Create A Network</strong>新建一个虚拟局域网<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/uX96rYytkTIPjL7.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 141151.png\"><br><strong>Base</strong>就是一些基础信息，要记住<em>Network ID</em>，这之后其他设备接入该虚拟局域网要用<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/lvD5Hd8gLYejK6y.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 141121.png\"><br>比较重要的是这个<strong>member</strong>，你之后往zerotier这个虚拟局域网里加入其他设备需要在这里授权<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/G1BiVUhOWa6P5gC.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 140134.png\"><br>如果有中转服务器，需要在这里添加路由，这样才能使你的设备连接通过这个中转服务器<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/DIXTnswv2aFC1yp.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 140004.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"zerotier-常用命令-Linux\"><a href=\"#zerotier-常用命令-Linux\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zerotier 常用命令(Linux)\"></a>zerotier 常用命令(Linux)</h1><p>1.安装zerotier</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">curl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-s</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">https://install.zerotier.com</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">|</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">bash</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span></code></pre></div><p>2.启动Zerotier</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">start</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-one.service</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span></code></pre></div><p>3.重启Zerotier</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">restart</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-one.service</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span></code></pre></div><p>4.设置开机自启动Zerotier</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">enable</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-one.service</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span></code></pre></div><p>5.查看服务状态</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">status</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">   </span></span></code></pre></div><p>or</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">info</span></span></code></pre></div><p>6.加入网络 </p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">join</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">16位虚拟网络I</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">D</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>7.离开网络 </p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">leave</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">16位虚拟网络I</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">D</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>8.查看所有的网络 </p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">listnetworks</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span></code></pre></div><p>9.显示详细信息</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">listpeers</span></span></code></pre></div><p>10.授权设备</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zerotier-cli</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">orbit</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">16位虚拟网络I</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">D</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">16位要授权的设备的唯一标识</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">符</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id=\"zerotier使用-windows\"><a href=\"#zerotier使用-windows\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zerotier使用(windows)\"></a>zerotier使用(windows)</h1><p>拥有图形界面，是个人应该都会用。</p>\n<p>简单介绍一下如何添加设备到你的虚拟局域网</p>\n<p>点击<strong>join new network</strong>,然后输入你的<strong>虚拟网络ID</strong>(16位码)，在去zerotier center确认授权即可<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/57uCyg8RZP3Lmb4.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 143018.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">WARNING</p>\n<p><p>zerotier windows端下载好了之后会自动缩到任务栏，要在任务栏操作</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"zerotier-效果\"><a href=\"#zerotier-效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zerotier 效果\"></a>zerotier 效果</h1><p>可以通过zerotier虚拟局域网下提供的虚拟ip地址去进行不同设备之间的通信，从而实现内网穿透。<br>如下我配置了两个设备进入我的虚拟局域网，这两个设备现实中不在同一个局域网内<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/QoZ3vXWcHfr7mN9.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 142050.png\"><br>在cmd中ping另个设备可以看到已经可以ping通了，延迟还可以，其实是我配了中转服务器的缘故<br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2024/03/06/u58C9g1rZxVObAm.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2024-03-06 142403.png\"><br>正常情况如果不能P2P直连的话就会走zerotier的免费planet根服务器，但是zerotier的planet根服务器是部署在国外的，这一来一去延迟就会超级高，大概500ms往上，几乎到了无法使用的地步，因此强烈建议搭一个zerotier的moon中转服务器（我之后会再出教程如何配置zerotier的moon中转服务器，并实现高分辨率低延迟远程办公）。</p>\n","text":"Zerotier简介zerotier是一个异地组网的solution，可以进行内网穿透从而实现远程办公，将公司、学校、家里的设备牢牢控制在自己手心里。 Zero...","permalink":"/post/Zerotier——内网穿透神器-for-free","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"IT","slug":"IT","count":4,"path":"api/categories/IT.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"tool","slug":"tool","count":2,"path":"api/tags/tool.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Zerotier%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Zerotier简介</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Zerotier%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Zerotier安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#zerotier-center%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">zerotier center配置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#zerotier-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4-Linux\"><span class=\"toc-text\">zerotier 常用命令(Linux)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#zerotier%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-windows\"><span class=\"toc-text\">zerotier使用(windows)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#zerotier-%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">zerotier 效果</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Yesord","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/avatar/Flametail.gif","link":"/","description":"猫军阀军校的一个四年级学牲。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Yesord","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/aoliba_believer","juejin":"","customs":{"Home":{"icon":"/img/Home.svg","link":"https://home.yesord.top/about/"},"Academic":{"icon":"/img/Academic.svg","link":"https://academic.yesord.top"},"Travelling":{"icon":"/img/tr